## Personal Life

Brown married Crystal Malone, and together they had four children. Crystal was notable for her own civil rights efforts, having challenged racial barriers in a college sorority during the 1940s. Brown's family legacy includes significant contributions to education and civil rights. :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}

